FBIS4-46379 "jptot024__l94056" JPRS-TOT-94-024-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 6 June 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA PALESTINIAN AFFAIRS Hamas Issues Leaflet on Jerusalem Hamas Issues Leaflet on Jerusalem TA0606073294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0405 GMT 6 Jun 94 TA0606073294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Excerpts] Palestinian leaders in the territories are focusing efforts on East Jerusalem, mainly in a bid to lift the closure which has separated the city from the rest of the territories. Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has distributed a leaflet in the territories calling for an exacerbation of the battle until Jerusalem is liberated. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports: [Begin Amir recording] [passage omitted] Hamas has also exhorted its followers to put an emphasis on the struggle over Jerusalem. In a special leaflet distributed in the territories yesterday, 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam members were called upon to step up activities against Israel until what the leaflet described as the liberation of all of the homeland, including Jerusalem. [passage omitted]
